! HTML Language Support

Provides syntax highlighting for HTML in code blocks.

!! Supported Content

* Fenced code blocks: ```` ```html ```` or ```` ```htm ````
* Typed blocks: `$$$.html` or `$$$text/html`
* Tiddlers with type `text/html`

!! Features

* Full HTML syntax highlighting with tag and attribute coloring
* Nested CSS in `<style>` tags
* Nested JavaScript in `<script>` tags
* Bracket matching and code folding
